{{Youmay|the [[Foodstuff/Legends|food product]]|[[military rank]]s, [[Police rank|law enforcement ranks]], or [[the Rank]], an [[Water/Legends|aquatic]] [[Death/Legends|dead]] zone}}
'''Rank''' was a type of food served onboard the ''[[Reasonable Doubt]]''. It came in buckets, sloshed, and had a gummy consistency. If desired, it could be bought extra gummy as well.

